noted for his long - running role as homer simpson on the animated television series the simpsons , he voices many other characters on the show , including abraham " grampa " simpson , barney gumble , krusty the clown , sideshow mel , groundskeeper willie , mayor quimby and hans moleman .

the emmys : in 1993 dan castellaneta won an emmy for voice - over for the " mr. plow " episode of this series

